data.eml:eml: A new species of Alsodes (Anura: Alsodidae) from Altos de Cantillana, central Chile

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Charrier, Andrés, Correa, Claudio, Castro, Camila, Méndez, Marco A. (2015): A new species of Alsodes (Anura: Alsodidae) from Altos de Cantillana, central Chile. Zootaxa 3915 (4): 540-550, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3915.4.5
